short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly search for tabs, bookmarks, history, and open it.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Page Starter can quickly search and open tabs, bookmarks, and access history, greatly improving the efficiency of page opening:

(1) when a large number of tabs are open, use Page Starter to quickly navigate to the specified tabs.
(2) when you want to open a bookmark, use Page Starter to quickly find and open the bookmark on a new page.
(3) you can also use Page Starter to retrieve the history and reopen it.
(4) cooperate with the default shortcut key Shift + Ctrl + P to improve efficiency again.

Please rest assured to use, Page Starter is completely free, will not collect any information from users.

---

Page Starter 能快速搜索和打开 标签页、书签、访问历史，极大提升页面打开效率：

（1）当打开的标签页非常多时，使用 Page Starter 可快速定位到指定标签页；
（2）当想打开书签时，使用 Page Starter 可快速找到并在新页面打开书签；
（3）使用 Page Starter 也可以检索历史记录，并重新打开；
（4）配合默认快捷键 Shift + Ctrl + P 使效率再次提升；

请放心使用，Page Starter 完全免费，不会收集用户任何信息。
